== Experience and Gold ==

=== EXP Distribution ===

```
Total EXP = Sum of all enemy EXP values
Each living party member receives: Total EXP / Living Members
```

=== Gold Distribution ===

```
Total Gold = Sum of all enemy Gold values
Party receives: Total Gold (shared pool)
```

